Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}总算是停了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:59.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不过这水一时消不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}每年都来，习惯了~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:03.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:05.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你就先去三叔那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:06.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}恩。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}见到老君帮我要个签名吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:10.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}诶，你还有这爱好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:13.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:14.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}怎么走呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:17.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那麻烦你咯~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}要抓紧哦！！ ！ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:21.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}知道啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}早知道应该搭个顺风鸟~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:45.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}老君是太上老君么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:47.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}算是原型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}跟故事里编的不大一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:50.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢〜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那也很厉害喽？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他住哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:56.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}应该不远~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:57.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}抓紧哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:19.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}就是这里么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}恩，对呀。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:32.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里什么都没有呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:54.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里是老君的灵质空间一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}蓝溪镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:04.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}天是白色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:18.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这就是神仙居住的地方么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:19.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:20.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}感觉怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}感觉不像神仙住的地方呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}像个古镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:26.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好像没人住呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:42.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}恩……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是很久没有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好可惜噢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里明明很漂亮呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}老君一定会喜欢这句话的~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊，到城门了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是要出去了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好美啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:18.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里是星夜湖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}新夜壶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:20.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里怎么是晚上呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里并没有特定的白天黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}都是由老君控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}看到前面那座山了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那就是老君山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他就住在山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢〜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊，两边的石壁上有雕像呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是借火岩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:42.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}雕的是老君与清凝仙子邂逅的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇…好浪漫啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:04:59.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}全是书呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}老君已经在此闭关了三十年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇……好宅啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}别乱说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那这三十年他都在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}沉迷ACG
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你们来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:18.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}见过老君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈，玄离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}难得你还肯来我这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}您说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好久不见了~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你就是老君么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:31.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你明明是个小孩子呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这是节能模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}连衣服都不合身嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}舒服就好~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}声音和样子完全不搭~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}声音是可以变的么么哒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}但毕竟我要维持我德高望重的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}已经崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你为什么这么宅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我曾立下誓言，百年内不得离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}啊，为什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我本来已经不愿提起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那就不用说了…	那是距（今多年前的一段悲伤往事）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:03.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊，对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}老君您能帮我签个名么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}打架损坏赔偿账单？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不…不是这样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我…我们还是先谈正事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那便随我入内阁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}小白~你在这等一下~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}好~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这次给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}谛听，你可知罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:33.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}关我屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}您客气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}说来话长…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:41.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}说快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}四百年前我将天明珠置于楼顶并立下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}只要有人有本事把它带出我的灵质空间便归他所有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}或带着天明珠来要求我做一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:48.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}讲完~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:49.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}这你都听懂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:52.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那你还让我去追它？	那你还让他去追我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我完全忘了这回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇，好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}作为四百年来唯一一个成功者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这也说明了你很有本事嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:01.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}因为您疏于防范呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}这也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:06.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}不过在妖化的谛听追逐下逃脱也不是那么简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:09.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好了，你是要选天明珠还是条件呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:13.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}这样他们真的会有感应么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}那就是缔听？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}我觉得我们搞不定耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}做好份内之事即可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:29.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}来者何人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an1}来不及了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:39.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an3}就畅通无阻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}全是宅物呢…
